OL,6,FThe Conservative Party manifesto
OL,7,Fpledges to introduce "Martyn's Law" to
OL,8,Fhelp protect against terror attacks
OL,9,Ffollowing a row over delays in making
OL,10,Fit law earlier.
OL,12,F'Martyn's Law' is named after , 29,
OL,13,Fwho was one of 22 people killed in the
OL,14,Fin May 2017.
OL,16,FThe new law would require venues and
OL,17,Flocal authorities in the UK to have
OL,18,Ftraining requirements and preventative
OL,19,Fplans against terror attacks.
