OL,3,CTories make 'Martyn's Law' a manifesto
OL,4,Cpledge
OL,6,FOn Tuesday 11 June, the Conservative
OL,7,FParty manifesto revisited the issue,
OL,8,Fstating: "We will urgently introduce
OL,9,FMartyn's Law, in tribute to Martyn
OL,10,FHett, who was tragically killed
OL,11,Falongside 21 others in the Manchester
OL,12,FArena terrorist attack in 2017.
OL,14,F"This will ensure premises are better
OL,15,Fprepared for terrorist attacks by
OL,16,Frequiring them to take proportionate
OL,17,Fsteps to mitigate risks."
