OL,3,CTories make 'Martyn's Law' a manifesto
OL,4,Cpledge
OL,6,FThe Tories say getting Martyn's Law
OL,7,Fenacted has taken longer than
OL,8,Fanticipated but, even though it might
OL,9,Fstraddle a General Election, they are
OL,10,Fcommitted to making it law.
OL,12,FMr Sunak said passing the law by the
OL,13,Fsummer recess will still be possible,
OL,14,Fif he is re-elected, because
OL,15,FParliament will reconvene with enough
OL,16,Ftime then to get the Bill through the
OL,17,FHouse of Commons.
OL,19,FThe Labour Party has said it will
OL,20,Fintroduce Martyn's Law as a "priority"
OL,21,Fif elected.
